This is a great video for all of those drag racing enthusiast out there! If you are one of them its a must get. In this movie you will find corvettes and mustang doing huge burnouts, and taking off bown the road. This video also includes evry make and model of car you can think of. There is excellent commentary throughout this amazing movie. Do you think you can geuss what the fastest street car is? To find out, watch this movie, The Fastest Street Car Shootout.
